{"tid":2389076,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賀錦麗突然現身地方電視台專訪 民主黨參議員:這不是團結合作","createTime":"2021-01-31T15:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T15:20:03.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58bcd8028191479b29cfc0ee5eca8dd1ef8c45e5","tid":2389076,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"美國副總統賀錦麗（Kamala Harris）本週接受美國地方媒體專訪，宣傳拜登（Joe Biden）政府的武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情紓困計劃，而賀錦麗安排行程時溝通不良的問題，也引發民主黨籍聯邦參議員曼欽（Joe Manchin）質疑「這不是團結」。<br />\n<br />\n據《福斯新聞》報導，賀錦麗本週現身西維吉尼亞州和亞利桑那州2州的當地電視台接受專訪，宣傳拜登政府的1.9兆美元（約53兆台幣）武漢肺炎疫情紓困計劃。該計劃將擴大失業保險，增加育兒稅收抵免，所有美國人也將收到1400美元（約4萬台幣）紓困金。<br />\n<br />\n西維吉尼亞州的民主黨聯邦參議員曼欽對於賀錦麗的突然現身感到十分意外，表示執政當局沒有任何人通知他副總統現身該州的行程，並暗示：「溝通不良有悖於拜登、賀錦麗所提倡的團結。」曼欽也表示：「我們尋求兩黨共治，我們必須團結合作，而這（缺乏溝通）不是團結合作。」<br />\n<br />\n對於拜登政府推出的紓困案，屬於民主黨溫和派的曼欽認為應該限定補助對象：「我們想幫助所有需要幫助的人，但如果一個人年薪25-30萬美元（約700-840萬台幣），我不認為他們有像那些年收入4-5萬美元（約110-139萬台幣）的人那麼需要這筆紓困金。」<br />\n<br />\n《福斯新聞》分析，賀錦麗接受地方媒體專訪，不確定是不是因為執政當局想給曼欽等地方政要施加壓力，迫使他們支持紓困案。<br />\n<br />\n白宮新聞秘書莎琪（Jen Psaki）對賀錦麗接受地方媒體專訪的舉動則解釋道：「我們希望把它（紓困計劃）呈現給所有美國人，而這（接受地方媒體專訪）正是這麼做的方式。」莎琪也補充道，賀錦麗未來可能會在更多州接受地方媒體專訪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3427399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3427399&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1Gyfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=69aee92b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3427399&h=c5bd6918\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3427399</a><br />\n<br />\nfox news:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/kamala-harris-tv-appearance-in-west-virginia-surprises-manchin-thats-not-working-together\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fkamala-harris-tv-appearance-in-west-virginia-surprises-manchin-thats-not-working-together&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1Gyfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=a995508a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fkamala-harris-tv-appearance-in-west-virginia-surprises-manchin-thats-not-working-together&h=644dc5bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/kamala-harris-tv-appearance-in-west-virginia-surprises-manchin-thats-not-working-together</a>"},{"pid":"efb9fdad0a3d716fdc10c5ba485b23dc102d6668","tid":2389076,"uid":37528,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"講乜撚呀，種族歧視呀？"},{"pid":"6ddcc8eb991d1ebff7107105935f60cd41ac2052","tid":2389076,"uid":156121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"可能唔係有違團結<br />\n係基本行政能力差 冇交帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d784efbb10c44c94658187b5ecc96ddd97e7877d","tid":2389076,"uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:16:06.000Z","msg":"民主黨式團結=大學group project式團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edae8968ce8e8903804d3b6ee2c4db0cb4bd2a19","tid":2389076,"uid":32325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"efb9fdad0a3d716fdc10c5ba485b23dc102d6668","tid":2389076,"uid":37528,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"講乜撚呀，種族歧視呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:17:32.000Z","msg":"思路正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d830cb0d1044953e524792552c87d70861383aa7","tid":2389076,"uid":214679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"唔跟劇本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}